<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards are promulgated pursuant to Article 70 of the Telecommunications Act (hereinafter referred to as this “Act”)
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Public Telecommunications Statutory Fee items include the fee for examinations, inspection and license of Type I and Type II Telecommunications Enterprises (Business) and to contribute to coastal station, ground-air digital communications station. The charge schedule are as attached.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fees for examinations and inspection should be paid upon application; and for license the fee should be paid when issued.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[I. Applicant should remit the Statutory Fee in the form of cash, check issued by bank, treasury check, draft to the National Communications Commission or local financial institutions.
II. The aforementioned check, treasury check or draft should be made payable to DGT.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Except for the case of over-payment, payment by mistake or by stipulation any other law provided, the payment shall not be returned after applicant pay for Statutory Fee by the Standards.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards shall become effective from the date of its promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
